to those monsters...

180
00:16:44,716 --> 00:16:45,884
I don't want them to kill him.

181
00:16:45,968 --> 00:16:48,136
They're going to kill him either way,
and you know that.

182
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:49,805
They won't if he turns himself in.

183
00:16:49,888 --> 00:16:52,766
- It's a trap! Tata, my God!
- Lower your voice.

184
00:16:52,850 --> 00:16:54,685
No! No, ma'am.

185
00:16:54,768 --> 00:17:01,191
I will not stay quiet when...
when I see you... betraying my son!

186
00:17:01,275 --> 00:17:05,153
I have never betrayed Pablo.
Let's make that very clear.

187
00:17:05,821 --> 00:17:08,991
We're locked in this hotel
as if it were a jail.

188
00:17:09,074 --> 00:17:11,118
We can't even leave the country.

189
00:17:12,619 --> 00:17:17,124
