196
00:17:58,999 --> 00:18:00,500
I'll tell them.

197
00:18:18,477 --> 00:18:21,438
We have intel
that Escobar is in this building.

198
00:18:22,189 --> 00:18:26,026
Listen up. I want you to do
what you can to get him alive.

199
00:18:26,735 --> 00:18:29,655
Escobar must be brought to justice
before the people of Colombia

200
00:18:29,738 --> 00:18:33,533
and answer for the atrocious crimes
he has committed against this nation.

201
00:18:34,242 --> 00:18:37,788
Now, if he resists...

202
00:18:38,497 --> 00:18:41,625
