You can't risk being seen, sir.

215
00:22:22,554 --> 00:22:24,681
This is my city, Limón.

216
00:22:28,643 --> 00:22:30,395
These are my people.

217
00:22:34,024 --> 00:22:37,277
Medellín will never betray me.

218
00:22:41,656 --> 00:22:44,034
