signal. It bounced off the water.

229
00:23:37,921 --> 00:23:41,591
I'm going to get the rolling papers
and clear my head.

230
00:23:42,717 --> 00:23:44,427
Give me the keys!

231
00:23:44,511 --> 00:23:47,180
- If you want, I'll go.
- Where are the sunglasses?

232
00:26:17,288 --> 00:26:20,541
- Hello, sir.
- Hello, how are you?

233
00:26:20,625 --> 00:26:23,128
